" geen derdeparty-inskrywings – net jou wallet en gratis dienste."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Sommige blaaier blokkeer derdeparty-skripte vir privaatheid. Hierdie proxy "
"laai skripte via jou eie bediener om hierdie blokke te omseil."

